'''法蘭克·懷特二世'''（{{lang-en|Frank White Jr.}}，{{bd|1950年|9月4日|}}），為美國職棒大聯盟的二壘手。18年職棒生涯皆效力於堪薩斯市皇家，他在退休後曾擔任過球評和球隊教練，目前是美國傑克森縣的縣長。
==職業生涯==
懷特在1973年升上大聯盟，起初他因為分擔掉了當家二壘手Cookie Rojas的出賽時間導致他不受球迷喜愛。不過之後他便和[[喬治·布列特|喬治·布列特]]共同出賽1914場比賽，一度寫下單一球隊的隊友所共同保持的共同出賽紀錄。這紀錄一直到1995年才被老虎隊的[[艾蘭·川默|艾蘭·川默]]和[[盧·懷泰克|盧·懷泰克]]打破。

懷特生涯一共入選5次明星賽，拿下8座金手套獎和1座銀棒獎。1977年，他曾連續出賽62場比賽無任何守備失誤。1980年，他拿下美聯冠軍賽的MVP。

懷特在1985年和1986年皆穩定輸出單季22轟，1985年世界大賽，大聯盟取消指定打擊，因此懷特便擔任中心棒次。1986年的明星賽，懷特在比賽中敲出一支陽春砲，幫助美聯拿下勝利。1990年，40歲的懷特宣布退休，留下2成55的打擊率，敲出160轟與886分打點。另外他生涯也曾兩度達成完全打擊。

==退休之後==
[[File:Kansas_City_Royals_-_20.png|thumb]]
退休後，懷特先後在紅襪和皇家隊擔任一壘指導教練。他原本要在2007年後接任皇家隊總教練，<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.newspapers.com/clip/15470470/around_the_league/ |title=Around the League |newspaper=[[St._Louis_Post-Dispatch|St. Louis Post-Dispatch]] |date=August 3, 2007 |access-date=November 30, 2017 |via=newspapers.com |archive-date=2017-12-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171201044116/https://www.newspapers.com/clip/15470470/around_the_league/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>不過後來由[[特雷·希爾曼|特雷·希爾曼]]接任，而懷特則轉居幕後。<ref>Paylor, Terez A. (2011-01-30) [http://www.kansascity.com/2011/01/30/2620942/frank-white-steps-down-from-advisory.html Frank White resigns front-office role with Royals]. KansasCity.com. Retrieved on 2011-12-04. {{webarchive |url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110203011329/http://www.kansascity.com/2011/01/30/2620942/frank-white-steps-down-from-advisory.html |date=February 3, 2011 }}</ref>目前他在美國職業棒協的堪薩斯市君王隊擔任一壘指導教練。<ref>{{cite web |title=Frank White takes the field with the T-Bones |url=http://www.kshb.com/sports/baseball/frank-white-takes-the-field-with-the-t-bones |work=kctv5.com |date=May 9, 2012 |access-date=May 26, 2017 |archive-date=2017-12-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171201033835/http://www.kshb.com/sports/baseball/frank-white-takes-the-field-with-the-t-bones |dead-url=no }}</ref>
==邁入政壇==
2014年，懷特加入民主黨，並通過黨內初選獲得競選傑克森縣縣長的資格。<ref>[http://www.kctv5.com/story/24841525/royals-hall-of-famer-frank-white-running-for-jackson-county-legislature Royals Hall of Famer Frank White running for Jackson County Legislature] {{Wayback|url=http://www.kctv5.com/story/24841525/royals-hall-of-famer-frank-white-running-for-jackson-county-legislature |date=20171201043844 }}. kctv5.com. Retrieved on 2014-06-27.</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.sportingnews.com/other-sports/news/election-day-2014-midterm-elections-sports-politics-frank-white-pete-ricketts-royals-cubs/1fcbmmgcwwvsh1th1p5hrf04rv |title=Election Day: Royals legend Frank White earns political victory |first=Tom |last=Gatto |website=sportingnews.com |date=November 5, 2014 |access-date=November 30, 2017 |archive-date=2017-12-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171201032452/http://www.sportingnews.com/other-sports/news/election-day-2014-midterm-elections-sports-politics-frank-white-pete-ricketts-royals-cubs/1fcbmmgcwwvsh1th1p5hrf04rv |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2016年1月11日，懷特被選為該縣縣長。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.jacksongov.org/395/County-Executive |title=County Executive Frank White Jr. |website=jacksongov.org |date=January 11, 2016 |access-date=2021-03-15 |archive-date=2021-02-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210218162653/https://www.jacksongov.org/395/County-Executive |dead-url=no }}</ref>之後他又再連任一次。<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.kansascity.com/news/politics-government/election/article113515723.html |title=Frank White elected Jackson County executive; Mike Sharp wins third term as sheriff |first=Mike |last=Hendricks |newspaper=[[The_Kansas_City_Star|The Kansas City Star]] |date=November 8, 2016 |access-date=November 30, 2017 |archive-date=2020-11-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201123082448/https://www.kansascity.com/news/politics-government/election/article113515723.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>
